  "rulesTichuSpecialMahjongLine1": "The player holding this card leads the very first trick.",
  "rulesTichuSpecialMahjongLine2": "When playing the Mahjong, you may declare a number (2–14). The next player must include that number in their combination if they have it (ignored if they don't).",
  "rulesTichuSpecialDogTitle": "Dog",
  "rulesTichuSpecialDogLine1": "Can only be played when leading. Immediately passes the lead to your partner.",
